commit 52388937846f9c7c0b078f93d68c7977451ff1d7
Author: vchat-meme-blip <limeikenji@gmail.com>
Date:   Sat Mar 28 22:51:39 2026 +0200

    feat(local-llm): replace PRoot/HTTP inference with fllama NDK
    
    Replaces the broken llama-server binary download + npm/node-llama-cpp
    approach with fllama — a Flutter plugin wrapping llama.cpp via Android
    NDK. Local inference now runs natively on ARM64 with no PRoot dependency,
    no binary download, and no HTTP sidecar.
    
    Key changes:
    - local_llm_service: remove all http/npm/tmux methods; add _activateFllama()
      that simply stores the host GGUF path and sets status=ready; add chat()
      for multi-turn history; testInference/analyseVideoFrames use fllamaChat()
    - gateway_service: local-llm branch calls LocalLlmService.chat() directly;
      sendVisionMessage uses LocalLlmService.analyseVideoFrames() instead of :8081
    - constants.dart: drop getLlamaServerZipUrl() / _llamaBuild (broken 404)
    - android/build.gradle.kts: pin ndkVersion to 27.0.12077973 for fllama
    - pubspec.yaml: add fllama git dependency
    
    Co-Authored-By: Claude Sonnet 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>

