commit a540b458c06de733def090af2ce6e4c10d6c7d4a
Author: vchat-meme-blip <limeikenji@gmail.com>
Date:   Fri Mar 27 18:10:50 2026 +0200

    fix(llm): detect model files via host filesystem instead of PRoot
    
    Replace NativeBridge.runInProot('test -f ...') with direct Dart File
    checks on the host path ({appSupportDir}/rootfs + prootModelPath).
    
    PRoot calls silently return false on timeout/exception, causing
    _isModelInstalled and _isMmProjInstalled to always return false
    and trigger a full re-download on every session start.
    Host filesystem check is instant, never times out, and correctly
    skips the download when the GGUF is already present.
    
    Co-Authored-By: Claude Sonnet 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>

