    fix(llm): health check port mismatch — node-llama-cpp approach uses port 18789 not 8081
    
    The node-llama-cpp backend patches openclaw.json and reloads the gateway
    (port 18789). Nothing runs on 8081 with this approach, so the old health
    check looped 30×3s and always timed out.
    
