commit 34b5bc7423b41ee6cad323b2e63ff01d5ef02e61
Author: vchat-meme-blip <limeikenji@gmail.com>
Date:   Fri Mar 27 14:31:43 2026 +0200

    fix(llama+skills): binary validation, static link, crash log surfacing, MoltLaunch nav
    
    local_llm_service.dart:
    - _isBinaryInstalled: add --version sanity check — size-only check misses
      dynamically-linked binaries whose shared libs were deleted with source tree;
      non-zero exit now triggers automatic recompile
    - cmake Stage 3: add -DBUILD_SHARED_LIBS=OFF — forces fully static binary
      so it runs without the source tree present after cleanup
    - _startServer crash script: tail last 30 lines of llama-server.log after
      "Process died immediately" so the actual crash reason is visible in the UI
    
    skills_manager.dart:
    - _MoltLaunchBanner non-installed state: add GestureDetector + chevron, wire
      onTap to onRegister (was untapped static container — nothing happened on press)
    - Change onRegister callback to onNavigate('molt-launch') so banner opens
      AgentWorkPage instead of showing the coming-soon sheet
    - Update banner subtitle to describe the feature, not its registry status
    
    Co-Authored-By: Claude Sonnet 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>

